Don't know if there is any special technique other than the normal....<br>
<br>
1 - Tash your pet prior to charm<br>
<br>
2 - Root your victim and keep him rooted<br>
<br>
3 - Snaring pet with something like A Ball of Burlap Yarn really helps.<br>
<br>
4 - Expect breaks, raise your Charisma as it will help.<br>
<br>
5 - Using a giant as a pet will be tough as its a great way to reset things.<br>
<br>
6 - Always have SoW<br>
<br>
7 - Slow Victim, haste pet<br>
<br>
